ys later when chairman steve garban resigned his position in january  he relinquished the position to the bank of new york mellon executive karen peetz but he has continued to serve on the board surma served as a director of bny mellon until april  in  his reported compensation as a director of bny mellon was  surma is involved with education and community development in pittsburgh surma became an honorary member of the national society of black engineers nsbe in citation needed surma received the american iron and steel institutes elbert gary medal in  surma retired as chief executive officer of united states steel on august   he will continue to serve as executive chairman of the board of directors until december   when he will retire from the company and the board compensationedit while ceo of united states steel in  john p surma earned a total compensation of  which included a base salary of  a cash bonus of  stocks granted of  options granted of  and other compensation of  in  he requested a  salary reduction and more than  reduction in his compensation package citing the difficult business environment from june   to may   with surma at the helm us steels stock value plummeted by  pittsburgh penguinsedit surma is a minority owner of the pittsburgh penguins of the national hockey league with a share estimated in  of  million notesedit “john p surma jr – president and chief executive officer” united states steel corporation biography  at the wayback machine archived march   referencesedit  httpwwwbaptisthomessocietyorgassetsfilesalongthejourneybhspratjpdf  staff  january  people on the move pittsburgh postgazette business p b   february  us steel corporation interview with john p surma the wall street transcript  pp–  staff  surma assumes uss ceo post usher remains chairman metal producing  processing  p  guzzo maria  november  uss surma will add chairmans post as usher opts for early out american metal market  p  boselovic len  november  us steels ceo surma to b