ary medal in  surma retired as chief executive officer of united states steel on august   he will continue to serve as executive chairman of the board of directors until december   when he will retire from the company and the board compensationedit while ceo of united states steel in  john p surma earned a total compensation of  which included a base salary of  a cash bonus of  stocks granted of  options granted of  and other compensation of  in  he requested a  salary reduction and more than  reduction in his compensation package citing the difficult business environment from june   to may   with surma at the helm us steels stock value plummeted by  pittsburgh penguinsedit surma is a minority owner of the pittsburgh penguins of the national hockey league with a share estimated in  of  million notesedit “john p surma jr – president and chief executive officer” united states steel corporation biography  at the wayback machine archived march   referencesedit  httpwwwbaptisthomessocietyorgassetsfilesalongthejourneybhspratjpdf  staff  january  people on the move pittsburgh postgazette business p b   february  us steel corporation interview with john p surma the wall street transcript  pp–  staff  surma assumes uss ceo post usher remains chairman metal producing  processing  p  guzzo maria  november  uss surma will add chairmans post as usher opts for early out american metal market  p  boselovic len  november  us steels ceo surma to become chairman pittsburgh postgazette business p e  mas renate f  october  u s steels surma tapped by iisi board to succeed dolle as chairman american metal market  p   van natta jr don  april  fight on state retrieved  january    rubinkam michael  exchairman of penn state board of trustees quits retrieved  january    forbes retrieved  january    robertson scott  may  us steels surma awarded aisis gary medal american metal market  p  executive biographies united states steel september      ceo compensation for john p surma equilarcom  us st